𝐑𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐳𝐯𝐨𝐮𝐬 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐑𝐚𝐀𝐛𝐭𝐚 𝐁𝐫𝐢𝐝𝐞 : 𝐍𝐚𝐦𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐢𝐩𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐢 ✨

Styling a bride is always full of excitement. 
Though I have done that 100s of times but it always feels new & fresh to me. 
Every bride to be have her own excitement/queries/anxieties once she walks into RaAbta store. 
But what makes me feel most happy & satisfied that she goes back only with a content heart. 
What follows is a lifetime bond full of warmth, compliments and some great memories. 

Coming up next Our Bubbly Bride @tripathi_namrata ✨
She is also the face of Our cherished campaign PALKI
and after which we reconnected for her wedding. 
Styling Namrata was full of fun. 
We could delightfully achieve the grand look she had in mind for her wedding.
- RAHUL LUTHRA
